Assisting FCE Dept with daily tasks to ensure smooth delivery of FCE lessons
Preparing food Ingredients for FCE Lessons
Monitoring stock level of food ingredients and reminding FCE department to replenish stock when required
Ensuring Safety compliance within kitchen at all times
Ensuring all equipment /utensils are clean and stored properly
Washing of School table clothes,bedsheets,uniform etc
Operating basic kitchen equipment safely
Any other Duties assigned by School leaders 

